---

<Layout
  title="Help & Guide - Food Diary App"
  description="Learn about our food diary app designed to make tracking your meals simple, fast, and meaningful."
  showBottomNav={true}
  showTopNav={true}
  wideContent={true}
>
  <main class="w-full py-6 sm:py-10 lg:py-12">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6">
          About
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8 sm:mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          This food diary app is designed to make tracking your meals simple, fast, and meaningful. Log your food in seconds, view clear nutritional insights, and build healthier habits without the overwhelm. Whether your goal is weight management, improved performance, or just better awareness of what you eat, this app helps you stay consistent, informed, and in control.
