              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">iOS (iPhone/iPad)</h3>
            </div>
            <ol class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 min-w-[24px]">1.</span>
                <span>Open this site in <strong>Safari</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 min-w-[24px]">2.</span>
                <span>Tap the Share button (‚ñ°‚Üë)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 min-w-[24px]">3.</span>
                <span>Scroll and tap <strong>"Add to Home Screen"</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 min-w-[24px]">4.</span>
                <span>Tap <strong>"Add"</strong> to confirm</span>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            ‚ú® Once installed, the app works offline and appears like a native app on your home screen!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Everything you need to know about using the app</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Getting Started -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">üöÄ</span>
          Getting Started
        </h3>
        <div class="divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow-sm">
          
          <details class="group p-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4">
              <span class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">How do I log my first meal?</span>
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
              <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Click any date on the calendar</p>
              <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Click the <strong>"+ Add Meal"</strong> button</p>
              <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Enter your food name (e.g., "Chicken Breast")</p>
              <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Add the amount (e.g., "150g" or "1 cup")</p>
              <p><strong>Step 5:</strong> (Optional) Add nutrition details like calories, protein, carbs, and fats</p>
              <p class="mt-3 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded p-2">üí° <strong>Tip:</strong> Start typing to see autocomplete suggestions from your food library!</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group p-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4">
              <span class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Where is my data stored?</span>
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              <p>All data is stored locally in your browser using IndexedDB, which is more reliable than regular storage. Your data stays <strong>100% private</strong> and is never sent to any servers.</p>
              <p class="mt-2 bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/30 rounded p-2">‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Important:</strong> Use the Export feature regularly to backup your data!</p>
            </div>
          </details>

