              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              <p>All entries for the same time (e.g., 8:00 AM) are automatically grouped together under a single time header. This keeps your log organized and makes it easy to see what you did at specific times. Click the time header to collapse or expand each group.</p>
