              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              <p>Use the <strong>Library</strong> to manage your food items, <strong>Settings</strong> to customize units and preferences, and <strong>Export</strong> to backup your data. All your entries are automatically saved and can be edited or deleted as needed.</p>
